00:37:23.790 --> 00:37:25.040
AUDIENCE: As a result
of writing this book,

00:37:25.040 --> 00:37:27.520
have you developed any more
intimate fondness for spiders?

00:37:27.520 --> 00:37:30.370
Do you keep any
spiders as pets now?

00:37:30.370 --> 00:37:35.250
LESLIE BRUNETTA: I don't keep
